                                                                <div class="panel-wrapper clearfix"><div class="panel"><div class="panel-inner"><div class="article-image-wrapper"><div class="article-image darken"><div class="minisite-wrapper"><span class="minisite-icon minisite-icon-it_life white"></span></div><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/life/7-eleven-concept-store-admiralty/"><img width="349" height="240" src="http://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/7-eleven-concept-store-3-349x240.jpg" class="attachment-grid-post size-grid-post wp-post-image" alt="7-eleven-concept-store-3" title="7-Eleven在金鐘開首個概念店　　設計唔似一般的7仔？" /></a></div></div><h2><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/life/7-eleven-concept-store-admiralty/">7-Eleven在金鐘開首個概念店　　設計唔似一般的7仔？</a></h2><div class="authorship"><span class="author">by <a href="http://www.winandmac.com/author/admin/">Dave</a></span><span class="date">on January 15, 2016</span></div><div class="excerpt"><div class="excerpt-text">大家去7-Eleven買東西的時候，通常很快就會離開。不過，大家若去到這間位於金鐘力寶中心的全新概念店，或許會想留多一陣。它是首間集café和便利店於一身，除提供健康的中西美食，同時發售7-Eleven便利店的零食、飲品、貨品以及服務項目等。</div></div></div></div></div><br class="clearer" /><div class="panel-wrapper clearfix"><div class="panel"><div class="panel-inner"><div class="article-image-wrapper"><div class="article-image darken"><div class="minisite-wrapper"><span class="minisite-icon minisite-icon-it_life white"></span></div><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/life/hongkong-airlines-new-protection/"><img width="349" height="240" src="http://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/hongkong-airlines-protection-guitar-349x240.jpg" class="attachment-grid-post size-grid-post wp-post-image" alt="hongkong-airlines-protection-guitar" title="香港航空寸爆國泰？　　正式推樂器保護箱" /></a></div></div><h2><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/life/hongkong-airlines-new-protection/">香港航空寸爆國泰？　　正式推樂器保護箱</a></h2><div class="authorship"><span class="author">by <a href="http://www.winandmac.com/author/admin/">Dave</a></span><span class="date">on January 15, 2016</span></div><div class="excerpt"><div class="excerpt-text">經常被寸因管理不善而乜乜乜的國泰航空，過往曾經因為不讓音樂人的樂器於寄艙時加入額外保護，令音樂人的樂器損毁。國泰至今似乎都沒有好好改善，相反香港航空卻第一個率先推出特製寄艙樂器保護箱，為音樂人而設。</div></div></div></div></div><br class="clearer" /><div class="panel-wrapper clearfix"><div class="panel"><div class="panel-inner"><div class="article-image-wrapper"><div class="article-image darken"><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/2016/01/mark-zuckerberg-lousy-neighbor/"><img width="349" height="240" src="http://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/mark-in-china-349x240.jpg" class="attachment-grid-post size-grid-post wp-post-image" alt="mark-in-china" title="Mark Zuckerberg鄰居忍不住投訴　　稱住係隔離好慘" srcset="http://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/mark-in-china-700x480.jpg 700w, http://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/mark-in-china-349x240.jpg 349w" sizes="(max-width: 349px) 100vw, 349px" /></a></div></div><h2><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/2016/01/mark-zuckerberg-lousy-neighbor/">Mark Zuckerberg鄰居忍不住投訴　　稱住係隔離好慘</a></h2><div class="authorship"><span class="author">by <a href="http://www.winandmac.com/author/admin/">Dave</a></span><span class="date">on January 15, 2016</span></div><div class="excerpt"><div class="excerpt-text">若果你的鄰居是名人，甚至乎是Mark Zuckerberg，你會覺得高興抑或是悲慘？目前住在其附近的鄰居，向同區的居民發出信件，稱Mark Zuckerberg住在隔離對他們造成困擾。</div></div></div></div></div><br class="clearer" /><div class="panel-wrapper clearfix"><div class="panel"><div class="panel-inner"><div class="article-image-wrapper"><div class="article-image darken"><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/2016/01/qualcomm-snapdragon-820-by-samsung/"><img width="349" height="240" src="http://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/qualcomm-devices-349x240.jpg" class="attachment-grid-post size-grid-post wp-post-image" alt="qualcomm-devices" title="未來的Qualcomm Snapdragon 820　　也將由Samsung生產了！" /></a></div></div><h2><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/2016/01/qualcomm-snapdragon-820-by-samsung/">未來的Qualcomm Snapdragon 820　　也將由Samsung生產了！</a></h2><div class="authorship"><span class="author">by <a href="http://www.winandmac.com/author/admin/">Dave</a></span><span class="date">on January 15, 2016</span></div><div class="excerpt"><div class="excerpt-text">目前大家使用iPhone的時候，當中也有使用Samsung的處理器晶片。未來，若果使用Snapdragon的android手機，結果也可能無法脫離Samsung。因為，未來的Samsung也會協助生產Qualcomm Snapdragon 820處理器。</div></div></div></div></div><br class="clearer" /><div class="panel-wrapper clearfix"><div class="panel"><div class="panel-inner"><div class="article-image-wrapper"><div class="article-image darken"><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/2016/01/netflix-will-block-vpn-proxy/"><img width="349" height="240" src="http://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/netflix-vpn-349x240.jpg" class="attachment-grid-post size-grid-post wp-post-image" alt="netflix-vpn" title="大鑊！Netflix表明即將用高科技封鎖VPN　　香港用家仲可以睇乜呀！？" /></a></div></div><h2><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/2016/01/netflix-will-block-vpn-proxy/">大鑊！Netflix表明即將用高科技封鎖VPN　　香港用家仲可以睇乜呀！？</a></h2><div class="authorship"><span class="author">by <a href="http://www.winandmac.com/author/admin/">Dave</a></span><span class="date">on January 15, 2016</span></div><div class="excerpt"><div class="excerpt-text">Netflix未在香港和亞洲推出時，很多人其實都有用VPN或其他Proxy工具去睇。Netflix過往還在公開場合提到有關事情，稱VPN對他們的傷害不大，反正理論上都是合法的用家。可是，Netflix近日在香港和全球不同地方推出後，官方終於正式宣佈，會用進階的方法，去封鎖所有使用VPN或Proxy服務的用家。</div></div></div></div></div><br class="clearer" /><div class="panel-wrapper clearfix"><div class="panel"><div class="panel-inner"><div class="article-image-wrapper"><div class="article-image darken"><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/2016/01/siri-beatbox/"><img width="349" height="240" src="http://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/siri-beatbox-349x240.jpg" class="attachment-grid-post size-grid-post wp-post-image" alt="siri-beatbox" title="Siri最近練好Beatbox　　大家想聽一聽嗎？" /></a></div></div><h2><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/2016/01/siri-beatbox/">Siri最近練好Beatbox　　大家想聽一聽嗎？</a></h2><div class="authorship"><span class="author">by <a href="http://www.winandmac.com/author/admin/">Dave</a></span><span class="date">on January 15, 2016</span></div><div class="excerpt"><div class="excerpt-text">Siri每隔一段時間，就會為我們帶來驚喜。最近，她就在練習Beatbox，有網友發現後拍片放上網，引起不少人瘋傳。想叫Siri beatbox其實很簡單，只要講到beatbox關鍵字就可以。小編試過用廣東話叫，似乎不太成功，但英文則沒有問題。</div></div></div></div></div><br class="clearer" /><div class="panel-wrapper clearfix"><div class="panel"><div class="panel-inner"><div class="article-image-wrapper"><div class="article-image darken"><div class="minisite-wrapper"><span class="minisite-icon minisite-icon-it_plus white"></span></div><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/plus/alan-rickman-harry-potter-rip/"><img width="349" height="240" src="http://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/rickman-349x240.jpg" class="attachment-grid-post size-grid-post wp-post-image" alt="rickman" title="哈利波特Alan Rickman逝世　　演石內卜教授為人所認識" /></a></div></div><h2><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/plus/alan-rickman-harry-potter-rip/">哈利波特Alan Rickman逝世　　演石內卜教授為人所認識</a></h2><div class="authorship"><span class="author">by <a href="http://www.winandmac.com/author/admin/">Dave</a></span><span class="date">on January 14, 2016</span></div><div class="excerpt"><div class="excerpt-text">英國演員Alan Rickman因飾演Harry Potter哈利波特系列的石內卜教授，為不少人認識和有深刻印象。他今天於倫敦因癌症逝世，享年69歲。英國多章報章都已經確認有關消息。</div></div></div></div></div><br class="clearer" /><div class="panel-wrapper clearfix"><div class="panel"><div class="panel-inner"><div class="article-image-wrapper"><div class="article-image darken"><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/2016/01/gopro-washing-machine/"><img width="349" height="240" src="http://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/go-pro-washing-machine-349x240.jpg" class="attachment-grid-post size-grid-post wp-post-image" alt="go-pro-washing-machine" title="把攝影機放進洗衣機　　究竟會出現什麼情況？" /></a></div></div><h2><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/2016/01/gopro-washing-machine/">把攝影機放進洗衣機　　究竟會出現什麼情況？</a></h2><div class="authorship"><span class="author">by <a href="http://www.winandmac.com/author/admin/">Dave</a></span><span class="date">on January 14, 2016</span></div><div class="excerpt"><div class="excerpt-text">很多人用GoPro拍過很多不同有趣的內容，今次我們想講一下的原因，是因為有人居然想到，把其攝影機放到洗衣機中。結果，會發生什麼情況？若果大家有空的，可以看看這段影片⋯</div></div></div></div></div><br class="clearer" /><div class="panel-wrapper clearfix"><div class="panel"><div class="panel-inner"><div class="article-image-wrapper"><div class="article-image darken"><div class="minisite-wrapper"><span class="minisite-icon minisite-icon-it_plus white"></span></div><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/plus/2016-policy-address-hongkong-is-completely-shit/"><img width="349" height="240" src="http://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/2016-policy-address-one-road-shit-349x240.jpg" class="attachment-grid-post size-grid-post wp-post-image" alt="2016-policy-address-one-road-shit" title="2016施政報告發表後　　才發覺政府痴線真係無上限" /></a></div></div><h2><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/plus/2016-policy-address-hongkong-is-completely-shit/">2016施政報告發表後　　才發覺政府痴線真係無上限</a></h2><div class="authorship"><span class="author">by <a href="http://www.winandmac.com/author/admin/">Dave</a></span><span class="date">on January 14, 2016</span></div><div class="excerpt"><div class="excerpt-text">由網絡23條，到全民退保，再加上李波事件，配合日常生活開支愈來愈貴，但住的地方卻愈來愈細狀況下，本來以為香港已經好痴線。無諗過，「一帶一路」香港政府痴線真係可以痴得無上限。</div></div></div></div></div><br class="clearer" /><div class="panel-wrapper clearfix"><div class="panel"><div class="panel-inner"><div class="article-image-wrapper"><div class="article-image darken"><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/2016/01/apple-iad-advertising-business-giveup/"><img width="349" height="240" src="http://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/advertising-with-apple-iad-349x240.jpg" class="attachment-grid-post size-grid-post wp-post-image" alt="advertising-with-apple-iad" title="蘋果決定放棄過份控制iAd市場？！　　或將全面由「你」控制" /></a></div></div><h2><a href="http://www.winandmac.com/2016/01/apple-iad-advertising-business-giveup/">蘋果決定放棄過份控制iAd市場？！　　或將全面由「你」控制</a></h2><div class="authorship"><span class="author">by <a href="http://www.winandmac.com/author/admin/">Dave</a></span><span class="date">on January 14, 2016</span></div><div class="excerpt"><div class="excerpt-text">蘋果廣告iAd推出的時候，Steve Jobs還在生，當時他希望把廣告市場改變。可是，發展6年後，至今情況比Google和Facebook表現都差。消息指，蘋果終於決定停止內部的iAd銷售部門，讓一切都變得自動化。</div></div></div></div></div><br class="clearer" />                                
